Hilton Holds Colombo Hotel Management As State Takes Over Land

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e   a n d   A s a n t h a   S i r i m a n n e
-- 
2011-03-10T09:34:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/hilton-holds-colombo-hotel-management-as-state-takes-over-land.html
Hilton Hotels & Resorts is
maintaining a more than 20-year management agreement at Hilton
Colombo after the Sri Lankan government took over the land and
building of the property, the local company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  Hilton representatives will discuss the change in ownership
“with the relevant” parties while continuing normal business
operations at the hotel, Hilton Colombo said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
 anushao@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
